
My 2-word/6-nibble submission is:

--------------------------------------------
; http://ww1.microchip.com/downloads/en/DeviceDoc/40001239E.pdf
;
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/PIC_microcontroller#Baseline_core_devices_.2812_bit.29

0000 001/0 0110 ; MOVWF GPIO
101/0 0000 0000 ; GOTO 0

.HEX:

:03 0000 00 026A00 (cs)
--------------------------------------------

This code should work on PIC10F200/202/204/206 (
http://www.microchip.com/ParamChartSearch/chart.aspx?branchID=1009&mid=10&lang=en&pageId=74)
- not that I have one available to test on.


